Padwa says "I use to be the 'shaman' for the garou that lived in this 
network of caves.  At first we consisted of the noble 'were-panther'.
Soon after the were-panthers made this place their home the 'were-wolf'
moved in.  For a time we lived in perfect harmony, but that was not
to last long.  The natural war between dogs and cats began gnawing at
our people.  A vicious and pointless 'war' broke out between the two 
groups of garou.  After years of pointless killing the were-panthers 
left the guild hall for other lands."
